reviewText: I really love this season it's absolutely brilliant and theres a lot of things happening in this survivor that the others didn't have. This is a great season to watch. I'm a big fan of the series but this is a classic. Please keep releasing more survivors on dvd. I'm ready for more, I want more survivors added to my dvd collection. Please…..
Title: Survivor, S16

reviewText: Survivor Micronesia is a great season of Survivor. This season is fans vs. favorites with a batch of some of the most beloved players in Survivor history returning. Plenty of Puppet Masters and wanna be Puppet Masters, you decide. Some really bad moves combined with really strategic moves makes this a great season.Parvati-10 Physical10 Social5 StrategicCirie-2 Physical10 Social9 StrategicOzzy-10 Physical4 Social4 StrategicJames-8 Physical2 Social2 StrategicAmanda-9 Physical7 Social7 StrategicNatalie- LunaticAlexis- UnderratedJonathan Penner- VillainEric- Easily Influenced
